# macOS / YandexDisk junk
.DS_Store
._*

# Fetched dependencies (run ./get_deps.sh) and per-step assembled build trees.
# These are reproducible from get_deps.sh + each step's assemble.sh, never committed.
/cores/
/deps/
build/

# Fetched ROM (run a step's get_rom.sh). The Spectrum ROM is redistributable for
# emulation but we still fetch it rather than ship it in the repo.
rom128.hex
combined128.rom
*.rom

# Build artifacts of the .z80 snapshot injector (zxinj): the embedded blob is
# generated from your own snapshot, the ELF is compiled. Snapshots aren't shipped.
zxinj/z80_blob.c
zxinj/snapshot.z80
zxinj/zxinj.elf
# Generated PCAP "armoured train" input (bootgen -process_bitstream bin from the .bit).
*.bit.bin

# Vivado / Vitis build artifacts.
# This repo commits only sources and prebuilt bitstreams; the full projects are
# built elsewhere, so the generated project tree never needs to land here.
*.jou
*.log
*.str
.Xil/
*.cache/
*.hw/
*.runs/
*.gen/
*.sim/
*.ip_user_files/
*.dcp
*.xpr
*.xsa
xsim.dir/
webtalk*.jou
webtalk*.log
usage_statistics_webtalk*
.jobs/

# Intentionally NOT ignored (these are the point of the repo):
#   *.bit / *.bin  — bitstreams and boot images
#   *.uf2          — Pico firmware
#   *.v *.sv *.vhd — HDL sources
#   *.xdc          — constraints
#   *.tcl *.sh     — build/flash scripts
#   *.hex          — memory init / ROM images
